OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1776243304
OL,3,CTwo drivers killed in crash
OL,5,FA woman and a man have been killed in
OL,6,Fa crash involving two cars.
OL,8,FThe drivers of both vehicles - a 29-
OL,9,Fyear-old woman and a 59-year-old man -
OL,10,Fdied at the scene of the collision,
OL,11,Fnear Frodsham, Cheshire.
OL,13,FEmergency services were called to the
OL,14,Fscene of the incident, involving a
OL,15,FVauxhall Corsa and Mini Cooper, on
OL,16,FManley Road, near New Pale Road and
OL,17,FYarrangall Green, just after 8am on
OL,18,FMonday, 13 April.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/4
