CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1776243304
OL,3,CTwo drivers killed in crash
OL,5,FThe families of those involved have
OL,6,Fbeen informed and are currently being
OL,7,Fsupported by specialist officers, a
OL,8,Fspokesperson from Cheshire Police said.
OL,10,FThe Serious Collision Investigations
OL,11,FUnit has now launched an appeal for
OL,12,Fanyone with information to come
OL,13,Fforward.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/4
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,400,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1776243304
OL,3,CTwo drivers killed in crash
OL,5,FSergeant Amy Hollis said: "We are
OL,6,Fworking to establish the full
OL,7,Fcircumstances surrounding this
OL,8,Fincident to determine what has
OL,9,Fhappened and, as part of our
OL,10,Fenquiries, we are now appealing to
OL,11,Fanyone who witnessed it to get in
OL,12,Ftouch with us.
OL,14,F"I would also like to ask the same of
OL,15,Fanyone who may happen to have any
OL,16,Fdashcam footage or additional
OL,17,Finformation which could aid us in our
OL,18,Fenquiries."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/4
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
