FL,400,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1776243304
OL,3,CTwo drivers killed in crash
OL,5,FSergeant Hollis added that the
OL,6,Ffamilies of those who have died have
OL,7,Frequested privacy during this "very
OL,8,Fdifficult time."
OL,10,F"Our thoughts remain with both of the
OL,11,Ffamilies of those who have sadly died
OL,12,Ffollowing this collision," she said.
OL,13,F"They remain supported by the
OL,14,FConstabulary."
OL,16,FOfficers are particularly keen to hear
OL,17,Ffrom anyone who may have dash-cam
OL,18,Ffootage of the incident or who
OL,19,Fwitnessed the collision as it happened.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/4
